			<article class="main container col4">
								<header class="maincol">
										<h1 class="pagetitle">On this Social Network, Sea Ice, Traditional Foods, and Wildlife Are Always Trending</h1>
										<h2 class="dek singlepagecontainer">Using an app developed by Inuit in Nunavut, Indigenous communities from Alaska to Greenland are harnessing data to make their own decisions.</h2>
										<section class="singlebyline singlepagecontainer">
						<h3 class="invis">Authored by</h3>
						by  
										<a href="https://hakaimagazine.com/profiles/hannah-hoag/" class="tagmanager" id="author_link_top" >Hannah Hoag</a>								<br/>
												</section>
					 
					<aside class="singlebydatewords singlepagecontainer">
						<h3 class="invis">Wordcount</h3>
						February 15, 2024 | 950 words, about 4 minutes					</aside>
