						<li><a class="icons icon-icons_email-top-share tagmanager" title="Share by Email" href="mailto:?subject=Sharing a story from Hakai Magazine&body=I thought you might find this story interesting:%0D%0A%0D%0AOn this Social Network, Sea Ice, Traditional Foods, and Wildlife Are Always Trending%0D%0AUsing an app developed by Inuit in Nunavut, Indigenous communities from Alaska to Greenland are harnessing data to make their own decisions.%0D%0Ahttps://hakaimagazine.com/news/on-this-social-network-sea-ice-traditional-foods-and-wildlife-are-always-trending/" target="_blank"><span>Share by Email</span></a></li>



